      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation across three mesh refinement levels (coarse ~180k elements, medium ~420k, fine ~950k). GCI values: stiffness 0.8%, yield force 1.1%, F@40mm 1.2%. Discretization error negligible relative to experimental variability."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals below 1e-5; energy balance error below 0.1%.",
      "rationale": "Direct sparse solver employed for linear phases; Newton-Raphson iteration for contact nonlinearity. Energy balance error 0.04%. No convergence warnings in any of the 11 simulation runs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of simulation setup; documented simulation control plan reviewed by second analyst.",
      "rationale": "Simulation control plan reviewed by independent senior analyst. Boundary conditions, load application, and material assignments independently verified. No discrepancies identified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model captures nonlinear plastic deformation of titanium alloy; contact formulation appropriate for screw-rod interface.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity (Ti-6Al-4V) calibrated against coupon tensile data. Augmented Lagrangian contact with friction coefficient 0.2 at screw-rod interface. Model form supported by published FEA literature for ASTM F1717 constructs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
