      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA inputs traceable to measured experimental inputs; no unmatched parameters between simulation and test.",
      "rationale": "All FEA material inputs derived from same material lots as test constructs. Boundary conditions replicate test fixture geometry confirmed by fixture drawings. Cross-head displacement and reaction force outputs matched to experimental measurement channels."
    },
