      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI differences < 10% and E/uval < 1.96 for all three primary quantities of interest.",
      "rationale": "Stiffness: FEA 312 N/mm vs. experimental mean 308 N/mm (1.3% diff, E/uval 0.41). Yield force: 1842 N vs. 1819 N (1.3%, E/uval 0.38). F@40mm: 2104 N vs. 2088 N (0.8%, E/uval 0.29). All acceptance criteria met."
    },
