    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required credibility level. Test conditions factor (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) accepted as documented limitation consistent with ASTM F1717 single-condition prescription. Overall model credibility sufficient for intended regulatory submission supporting 510(k) clearance of non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
